bout" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent">About</a><ul><li id="main-menu-link-content1063f1c6-3f8b-4d7b-9390-386192b1a298" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/about/organization/board" class="sf-depth-2">Governing Board</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-contentd1190240-14af-41e7-991b-27a6bbe5724d" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/about/staff" class="sf-depth-2">Staff directory</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content4fae7d8a-2c69-44a4-aa00-c6cec96502f1" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/about/library" class="sf-depth-2">Library</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content1dbba8a4-60f2-4bf5-8556-865783825d51" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/about/support_sipri" class="sf-depth-2">Support SIPRI</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-contenta0ce100a-3451-4aab-9798-da6dc59733e8" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/about/vacancies" class="sf-depth-2">Vacancies</a></li></ul></li>
